        </mj-text>
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/howard-lutnick-white-house-2025.png" alt="Howard Lutnick stands at the White House" href="https://www.longandshort.com" />
